                            <h3>Water is health, water is life</h3>
                            <p>For Sophon, there was nothing beautiful about the water-related burdens she endured much
                                of her life in rural Cambodia. She wanted to end those burdens for her son.</p>
                            <p>It is for women like Sophon, who aspire to give their babies a healthy start to a
                                beautiful life, that we created WaterCredit. With a small, affordable loan, Sophon and
                                her husband were able to pay for the construction of a rain storage tank and water tap
                                on their property. What was once unsafe to consume and took hours to collect is now
                                available outside their door.</p>
